-- ISDA Says to Rule on Elpida Memory Bankruptcy Credit Event
-- B y   A b i g a i l   M o s e s
-- 2012-02-27T14:59:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-27/isda-says-to-rule-on-elpida-memory-bankruptcy-credit-event.html
The International Swaps &
Derivatives Association said a group of dealers and investors
will rule if there has been a bankruptcy credit event that will
trigger credit-default swaps linked to  Elpida Memory Inc. (6665)   To contact the reporter on this story:
